This paper deals with deep neural networks and their compression, which is a topic that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper evaluates its approach on tasks related to image recognition and verification, which are also relevant to natural language processing (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.NE, followed by cs.AI and cs.CL.
